able to get it from them.

\n< Serena >....

"  I don't know what's going on, but I have achieved my goal anyway.\n  Let's go back to the inn and rest for today."

Serena: My health is good today. With this, I
should be able to handle any requests
without any problems.

to try looking for that so-called
monster scholar?
\n< Serena >Mmm...

prepare myself.

\n< Serena >Are you ready?

seat here, if you would.
\n< Serena >I'm here to intrude!
\n< Female >That's the reason.
\n< Serena >Haaaahhhh.......
\n< Female >I wonder what happened?

\n< Serena >No... it's nothing. I just had my own
expectations... and they didn't pan out.

\n< Serena >To summarize the story... you were engaged

\n< Serena >I explained to my partner that I have no

\n< Serena >But in reality, there is. However, I
thought that there was no way you would
understand if I stayed silent.

\n< Serena >However, my partner brought out a magic item
called the Unicorn Saddle... which
determines past dating experiences.

\n< Serena >I want you to ride this and prove that
you are truly a pure maiden...

\n< Female >How rude of a conversation is this! It
makes me angry just thinking about it!

\n< Female >There's no way you don't have any experience
with men at your age! Use common sense
and think logically!

\n< Serena >However, for an unmarried woman to have
interactions with men is considered a
crime of adultery.

\n< Serena >It's a serious crime. I've heard that
depending on the circumstances, it could
even lead to beheading or burning at the
stake.

\n< Female >Hoho, that's just a facade. Nowadays, there's
no one who takes things seriously like
that.
\n< Female >Yes, besides this stupid nobleman...!

\n< Female >...But even so, I can't let go of such a good
marriage proposal.

\n< Serena >So, to deceive the unicorn saddle, it's a

unique spirit herb...

\n< Female >Yes, researching was very difficult... but
this is where money and time come into
play!

\n< Female >If I think about how the next several
decades of my life will change, I won't
hesitate!

\n< Serena >I just need to procure that spirit herb,
right?

\n< Female >Please. I've heard that the habitat of the
spirit herb is deep in the forest. It is
said to be located at the end of
following the butterfly adorned with
blue phosphorescence.

\n< Female >But that place is also a dangerous zone
where monsters roam. It's very, very...
for a weak woman like me...

\n< Serena >Deep in the forest. The landmark is a blue
butterfly. Whether it's luring with
flower nectar... In any case, I
understand. I'll go gather it right
away.

\n< Female >Oh, are you leaving already? I thought
maybe we could have some tea together or
something.

\n< Serena >I'll pass. It's a simple request. I want it
done by today.

\n< Serena >It took quite a while just to listen to
all of this.

\n< Female >Oh my, ohoho, how rude of me. I got
carried away and started talking.

\n< Female >And that's because your manners and
behavior are perfect.

\n< Female >You've interpreted and responded to each of my
actions with meaning. It's been so
enjoyable... I couldn't help myself.

\n< Female >I wonder where you learned that? Your
family must have been very enthusiastic
about education.

\n< Female >Your face is elegant... It's such a waste to
see you being an adventurer in a rural
town like this.

\n< Female >I see. When this request is
accomplished... and when my marriage is
splendidly achieved...

\n< Female >Yes, I will definitely invite you to the
social circle.

\n< Female >If it's you, you should be able to serve
as a suitable companion for a noble. If
things go well, you could even become a
mistress... Depending on the family, you
might even be able to aim for the
position of a legal wife.

\n< Female >There is a single baron who lives a little
north of here. That person is quite a
catch, isn't he?

\n< Female >I will definitely introduce you, so
please do your best to successfully
complete the request.

\n< Serena >...If I were to tell my father that I want to
marry a baron, he would probably faint
on the spot.

\n< Female >Oh, I'm sorry. Your voice is so soft. What
did you say just now?
\n< Serena >It's nothing. Well then, I'll be going.

\n< Serena >Well... If it's this forest, it would be best
to leave the town from the south. Once
I'm ready, I'll head south.

\n< Serena >I can't appear in public wearing such a
